Dato' Saifuddin Abdullah, Malaysian Deputy Minister for Higher Education presents a public lecture at The Australian National University.Elected to the Malaysian parliament in 2008, Dato' Saifuddin Abdullah was previously the Secretary-General of the Malaysian Youth Council. He has written four books on Malaysian politics.
